para_trans: About opening a new article title
Maharashtra State Export Promotion Policy-2023
Special incentives for internal exporting components
Regarding the opening of a new account title to provide for this.
Government of Maharashtra
Industries, Energy, Labour and Mining Department
Government Decision No. Exports-2023 / Q. 193 / Industry-7
Mantralaya, Mumbai - 400 032.
The Proposal: -

The Maharashtra State Export Promotion Policy-2023 has been notified vide Government Decision dated 22/11/2023 and the policy provides for special incentives for exportable components under the policy.
Separate Head of Accounts launched to budget Rs 2,000 crore over the period
A proposal to do so was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:
Promotion of Export-Oriented Components in the State under Special Incentive for Export-Oriented Components
The Government is hereby approving the opening of the following head of accounts for budgeting the outlay for disbursement.
02. The said Government Decision No.B.V. / C of the Principal Accountant General (Accounts and Licensure), Mumbai-
1 / Department of Industry, Energy and Labour / UOR - 167/2023-24 1129, dated 30/01/2024

With the approval given under the letter, with the approval given under the Informal Reference No. 05 / Q. 1461, dated 05/01/2024 of the Planning Department and the Informal Reference No. 05/2024 Expenditure - 16,
Issuing with the date 10/01/2024 given.
